OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFacebook down: Zuckerberg  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologises for six-hour    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Foutage                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Facebook's founder Mark Zuckerberg has 
OL,6, apologised for the "disruption" caused 
OL,7, after its social media services went   
OL,8, down for almost six hours - impacting  
OL,9, more than 3.5bn users worldwide.       
OL,11,FThe billionaire said sorry after an    
OL,12,Finternal technical issue took Facebook,
OL,13,FMessenger, Whatsapp and Instagram      
OL,14,Foffline at about 16:00 GMT on Monday.  
OL,16,FThe scramble to bring it back online   
OL,17,Feventually succeeded at around 22:00.  
OL,19,FBut it is likely to increase scrutiny  
OL,20,Fof the social media giant's reach.     
